QuestData.Title: Silkwing Sabotage
QuestData.Description:
Moths. Who ever heard of something so... barbaric!
They are eating our crop and the mana wyrms do nothing to deter them.
You. You seem capable. Deter these creatures so we can complete our harvest on schedule.
Ahem. Please.
QuestData.RewardText: Much better. You have my thanks.
